description:
Apparently Tuxguitar's electric bass is labeled 'Picked Bass', which I only found out recently. Changed the bass instrument to electric bass. 

Unfortunately I still don't know how to reach those low notes normally, as even with a 4-string bass, Tuxguitar seems to only go as low as E2. The 24-fret capo lets me go lower than that to match the song, but I doubt that's actually how it's played. Would appreciate it if a bassist could contribute to this.
title: Keeper of Lust
